sort.desc:
 Sorting method that sectors use based on [value][0], which is the sum of children when not set. The default value 'desc' states for descending order, while it can also be set to be 'asc' for ascending order, or null for not sorting, or callback function like: 

    function(nodeA, nodeB) {
        return nodeA.getValue() - nodeB.getValue();
    }




